des:
If you have any problems when using this skill, you can contact us at the e-mail address: support@greenplux.com

Amazon Alexa and MIDILIGHT Smart home products work together to help you control the device in a simple and easy way.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.
It is not necessary to use the switch to adjust the light of the house: just talk to Alexa on Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to your MIDILIGHT Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "MIDILIGHT Smart" app in the Android or iOS App Store;
(2). Register your account in our "MIDILIGHT Smart" app;
(3). You must have one or more MIDILIGHT Smart devices available;
(4). Configure these devices in our MIDILIGHT Smart app and change the appropriate name for your devices that will be used in "MIDILIGHT Smart" skills;
(5). Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, iOS or Amazon Market;
(6). Configure Echo with the "Alexa" app;
(7). Look for the skill "MIDILIGHT Smart" in the skill category of the "Alexa" app;
(8). Click on "Enable MIDILIGHT Smart Skills" and you will be directed to the MIDILIGHT login page;
(9). Enter the username and password of your MIDILIGHT account, you will be redirected to the success page;
(10). Now the whole installation is finished.

You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on the kitchen light"
"Alexa, turn off the kitchen light"
"Alexa, lower the living room light"
"Alexa, raise the living room light"
"Alexa, set the living room light to 20 percent"
"Alexa, set the bedroom light to Blue"
"Alexa, turn on the room air conditioner"
